### API Reference > launchScanner - Launch Document Scanner

Source: https://context7.com/dariyd/react-native-document-scanner/llms.txt

Launches the native document scanner interface, allowing users to capture and process documents with automatic edge detection and perspective correction. The function returns a promise that resolves with scan results including image URIs, metadata, and optional base64 data.

